    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾经你担任助理的亚历杭德罗博士给你发来消息，邀请你前往他那座古老的庄园。你立刻启程，却完全不知道前方会发生什么。随着你面对的事件逐渐展开，你将慢慢揭开真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亚历杭德罗一直在进行一系列基因实验，但事情已经失控。他之所以向你求助，是因为你曾是他的助手，并且在你的领域非常出色。如果有办法解决这一切，那么除了你，没有人能够做到。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满丰富故事和谜题的 <i>Unprotected</i> 将恐怖与浓厚的氛围结合在一起，带来令人兴奋的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210750/extras/5efad9290cc62b6cf8112c07db4870e6.avif?t=1761930165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210750/extras_big/5efad9290cc62b6cf8112c07db4870e6.avif?t=1761930165 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210750/extras/dce37102eabec97cccc44168365e9910.avif?t=1761930165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210750/extras_big/dce37102eabec97cccc44168365e9910.webp?t=1761930165 width=1560 height=792 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210750/extras/0d5a353230d378e0b659952e79372e6c.avif?t=1761930165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210750/extras_big/0d5a353230d378e0b659952e79372e6c.webp?t=1761930165 width=1560 height=796 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210750/extras/7c9e76eb0957d093d6506caedbc5d5d6.avif?t=1761930165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210750/extras_big/7c9e76eb0957d093d6506caedbc5d5d6.avif?t=1761930165 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
